OL,7,FKris Jepson has been investigating
OL,8,Fhomelessness after being given
OL,9,Fexclusive access to data collected by
OL,10,Fthe Museum of Homelessness for this
OL,11,Fspecial report
OL,13,FOne homeless person dies every six
OL,14,Fhours according to analysis of new
OL,15,Ffigures, which shine a light on a
OL,16,Fgrowing problem blighting modern
OL,17,FBritain.
