OL,7,FFigures shared exclusively with ITV
OL,8,FNews by the Museum of Homelessness,
OL,9,Fwho analysed available data they
OL,10,Fobtained through Freedom of
OL,11,FInformation requests, show reported
OL,12,Fhomeless deaths rose last year by an
OL,13,Festimated 12.2% and have doubled in
OL,14,Fthe last five years.
OL,16,FDominic Drazdauskas is just one of an
OL,17,Festimated 1,747 reported homeless
OL,18,Fdeaths in 2023. Of those, like
OL,19,FDominic, 35% appear to be due to
OL,20,Fsubstance use and overdoses.
