OL,7,FDescribed as a loving, yet vulnerable
OL,8,Fyoung man, the 35-year-old died on
OL,9,FTeesside of an overdose last year,
OL,10,Fwhile he was homeless.
OL,12,FDominic's cousin believes that with
OL,13,Fthe right help, he might still be
OL,14,Falive. Now she is calling for more to
OL,15,Fbe done for those without a safe place
OL,16,Fto call home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/22
