OL,7,FAnnalise Argyle, his cousin, from
OL,8,FStockton, told ITV News: "He didn't
OL,9,Fhave a healthy lifestyle and whatever
OL,10,Fhealth issues he was suffering from
OL,11,Fwas compounded with the fact that he
OL,12,Fwas using drugs.
OL,14,F"He had nowhere to go. He'd burnt
OL,15,Fbridges everywhere. No one believed
OL,16,Fthat he'd be able to stop using and
OL,17,Fall he really needed was some support."
