OL,7,FAt the time of his death, Dominic was
OL,8,Fliving in homeless accommodation, but
OL,9,Fhis cousin, who works with women who
OL,10,Fregularly live in those settings, said
OL,11,Fshe has concerns over the level of
OL,12,Fsupport they offer.
OL,14,F"They're hidden...but people are dying
OL,16,F"I honestly think there should be like
OL,17,Frehabilitation support within those
OL,18,Fplaces and not just letting them be
OL,19,Fleft to their own devices," she
OL,20,Fcontinued.
