OL,7,F"Some people go in with a drug problem
OL,8,Fand they come out with a worse drug
OL,9,Fproblem, because it seems as if
OL,10,Fghettos are created, where everybody
OL,11,Fis just piled in together, because
OL,12,Fthere's no hope.
OL,14,F"They're hidden people, 'let's just
OL,15,Fput them all together and at least we
OL,16,Fknow where they are and they're off
OL,17,Fthe streets', but people are dying."
