OL,7,FEven in death, Dominic had little to
OL,8,Fhis name. Money was raised to buy
OL,9,Fflowers while the government paid for
OL,10,Fhis send-off.
OL,12,F"It was a pauper's funeral and it was
OL,13,Fvery, very sad to see that's what it
OL,14,Fcame to," added Annalise.
