OL,7,FAccording to their analysis of
OL,8,Favailable data, the number of people
OL,9,Fdying while homeless is growing - as
OL,10,Fis the rate of deaths among rough
OL,11,Fsleepers.
OL,13,FTheir analysis of available data
OL,14,Fsuggests reported homeless deaths on
OL,15,Fthe streets have risen by an estimated
OL,16,F42%, while the data suggests 20% more
OL,17,Fyoung homeless people are now taking
OL,18,Ftheir own lives.
