OL,4,C- Homeless deaths hit one every six
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FAnd living with the threat of
OL,8,Fpotentially fatal violence also
OL,9,Fappears a reality, with the report
OL,10,Festimating, from the charity's
OL,11,Fresearch of available data, that
OL,12,Fhomeless people are at least three
OL,13,Ftimes more likely to be murdered than
OL,14,Fthose with homes.
OL,16,FMatt Turtle, from the Museum of
OL,17,FHomelessness, is calling for a
OL,18,Fsystematic overhaul to prevent more
OL,19,Fhomeless deaths.
