OL,7,FThe report suggests, that in the North
OL,8,FEast last year alone, 51 homeless
OL,9,Fpeople died, earning this relatively
OL,10,Fsmall region - population-wise - the
OL,11,Fhighest rate of reported homeless
OL,12,Fdeaths in England outside of London.
OL,14,FAnd the numbers could be far higher
OL,15,Fdue to underreporting and other
OL,16,Ffactors. That is something that rings
OL,17,Ftrue for Middlesbrough woman Susan
OL,18,FGill.
