OL,7,FSusan ran the town's homeless cafe for
OL,8,F15 years, but in her last four, she
OL,9,Fsaid the loss became overwhelming.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News the impact "took its
OL,12,Ftoll" and left her "devastated",
OL,13,Fadding: "Because we'd had that many
OL,14,Fdeaths, we were still cooking a lot of
OL,15,Ffood that we were cooking and we had a
OL,16,Flot of waste at the end of the day,
OL,17,Fbecause we weren't getting the numbers
OL,18,Fthat we were catering for anymore."
