OL,7,FMr Turtle continued: "We don't do
OL,8,Freviews when people die at a council
OL,9,Flevel. So the information that we get
OL,10,Fis really, really patchy.
OL,12,F"Nearly one in ten of all the councils
OL,13,Fwe asked for information didn't have
OL,14,Fit, didn't record anything at all, but
OL,15,Funtil we have all local authorities,
OL,16,Fsupported by central government,
OL,17,Fproperly recording information, we're
OL,18,Fnot going to be able to make any
OL,19,Fimprovements.
