OL,7,F"We also need investment in rough
OL,8,Fsleeping services and we really need
OL,9,Fto properly regulate temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation so that when people do
OL,11,Fcome off the streets, that they're
OL,12,Fsafe and they can move on with their
OL,13,Flives."
OL,15,FThe report is calling for this kind of
OL,16,Fcare, alongside urgent policy reform,
OL,17,Fto ensure no one lives or dies without
OL,18,Fa roof over their heads.
OL,20,FBut the likelihood of that is
OL,21,Fdependent on political will.
